00:18:15.600 --> 00:18:19.260
We actually have six years
of post-program data too,

00:18:19.260 --> 00:18:25.680
which is, again, rare, and
here, quite interesting.

00:18:25.680 --> 00:18:28.530
Again, if you're thinking
about, which you may not,

