But we didn't design
the data gathering

00:18:56.670 --> 00:18:57.720
with this thing in mind.

00:18:57.720 --> 00:19:00.810
It just happened.

00:19:00.810 --> 00:19:05.150
I guess in that sense,
again, we just got lucky.

00:19:05.150 --> 00:19:07.070
We're going to look at
four kinds of outcomes,

00:19:07.070 --> 00:19:11.900
