00:19:20.520 --> 00:19:22.490
the reasons for borrowing--

00:19:22.490 --> 00:19:24.650
although I don't have
those slides for you

00:19:24.650 --> 00:19:29.430
here because money's
potentially fungible.

00:19:29.430 --> 00:19:32.970
We do look at interest
rates default and so on.

00:19:32.970 --> 00:19:36.900
We have consumption broken
down in these annual data,

00:19:36.900 --> 00:19:43.180
by the way, into
these categories.

