And again, we have
some ability to look

00:20:44.410 --> 00:20:48.040
at female headed as opposed
to male headed households.

00:20:52.240 --> 00:20:56.330
OK, what's an outcome?

00:20:56.330 --> 00:21:01.130
y for household n at date t.

00:21:01.130 --> 00:21:06.260
This is like imagine running,
oh, my god, a simple-minded OLS

00:21:06.260 --> 00:21:12.140
regression, the way people
