In fact, arguably there seems to
be almost an amplifier effect,

00:26:20.110 --> 00:26:22.570
but more weakly.

00:26:22.570 --> 00:26:25.480
Short-term credit goes
up, for sure, one to one.

00:26:25.480 --> 00:26:26.830
