00:26:26.830 --> 00:26:31.750
I mean, this is this like a huge
spike in the financial system.

00:26:31.750 --> 00:26:34.420
And it didn't go down.

00:26:34.420 --> 00:26:36.610
That part doesn't go
down subsequently.

00:26:36.610 --> 00:26:37.133
Yep.

